{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/488470/extras/Shaman_Big.gif?t=1731408710\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Shaman</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the wilderness with the Shaman. This elemental manipulator uses the forces of nature to his advantage and always has a tool for any situation. His skillset combines the talents of an elementalist with the chieftain\u2019s mastery, binding his powers to totems that aid him in battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Playstyle</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Shaman offers diverse playstyles, from continuously conjuring twisters and summoning meteor storms to taking a more passive approach by letting totems or spirit wolves do the fighting for him.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Recommended for:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players who enjoy a versatile caster capable of adapting to various scenarios.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Those who wish to conjure an army to fight on their behalf.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Anyone eager to master the elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Storm, Earth, and Fire, heed my call!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/488470/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731408710","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/488470/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1731408710","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/488470/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731408710","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/488470/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731408710","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-play